Global Artificial Grass Groomer Market Insights
Artificial Grass Groomer Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Artificial Grass Groomer Market Overview
The artificial grass groomer market is expected to witness steady growth over the forecast period. The global market value was valued at USD 95 million in 2024 and is projected to expand at a CAGR of 4.5% from 2024 to 2032. This growth is driven by the increasing demand for artificial grass in residential, commercial, and sports applications, along with the rising adoption of artificial turf maintenance products. Grooming tools enhance the longevity and appearance of synthetic turf, ensuring it stays in top condition throughout the year. Key players in the industry include brands offering a wide range of grooming solutions designed to provide optimal performance and durability.

